## üß≠ **Outline**

### **Front Matter**

* **Preface:** Why curvature learns to prefer.
* **Diagrammatic Overview:** From thermodynamic connection (Book 6) to valuated geometry.
* **Reading Note:** Replace ‚Äúforce‚Äù with ‚Äúconcern‚Äù; the metric is an index of care.

